<h2><i>All you need to know</i> </h2>

<p>
<div>Coffee is a brewed drink prepared</div> from roasted coffee beans, the seeds of berries from certain flowering plants in the Coffea genus. From the coffee fruit, the seeds are separated to produce a stable, raw product: unroasted green coffee. 
</p>

<p>
<span>The seeds are then roasted,</span> a process which transforms them into a consumable product:<hr> roasted coffee, which is ground into fine particles that are typically steeped in hot water before being filtered out, producing a cup of coffee.
</p>

